## Merge Manager: Hussein Al Salami (746006849)

## Project Structure
- `backend/` - Spring Boot application (Java, Spring Data JPA, MySQL)
- `frontend/` - Static HTML/CSS/JS pages using Bootstrap 5 and fetch() API
- `database/` - SQL seed data file (data.sql)

## REST API Endpoints

### Drop Off Locations (Hussein Al Salami)
- GET    /api/locations
- GET    /api/locations/{id}
- GET    /api/locations/search?name=xxx
- POST   /api/locations
- PUT    /api/locations/{id}
- DELETE /api/locations/{id}

### Users (Hussein Al Salami)
- GET    /api/users
- GET    /api/users/{id}
- GET    /api/users/search?email=xxx
- POST   /api/users
- PUT    /api/users/{id}
- DELETE /api/users/{id}

### Recycling Items (Saif Alshamali)
- GET    /api/items
- GET    /api/items/{id}
- GET    /api/items/search?name=xxx
- POST   /api/items
- PUT    /api/items/{id}
- DELETE /api/items/{id}

### Recycling Logs (Naren Karthik)
- GET    /api/logs
- GET    /api/logs/{id}
- GET    /api/logs/search?userId=xxx
- POST   /api/logs
- PUT    /api/logs/{id}
- DELETE /api/logs/{id}

## Database
